query:
SELECT 
                COUNT(*) as total,
                COUNT(CASE WHEN exit_code = 0 THEN 1 END) as successful,
                COUNT(CASE WHEN exit_code != 0 THEN 1 END) as failed,
                COUNT(DISTINCT command) as unique_commands,
                AVG(duration_ms) as avg_duration
            FROM commands
            WHERE timestamp >= ?
